Subject: Comic Jam
Description: What happens when you take a hand full of comics artists, arm them with paper and sharpies, and prompt them to draw a comic in an unrealistic timespan? No this isn't the riddle of the Sphinx! This is an interactive game that will push these artists to the brink, test their abilities and provide some serious laughs! Bring your sass, clever wit and sense of humor...cause it's you that suggests what they draw!  Speakers include:BluRaven C. Houvener, Crystal Mielcarek, Emily Zelasko - Track: Comics  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
